HEADWORD: Proposer
<hw>Pro*pos"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
proposes or offers anything for consideration or adoption.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A speaker; an orator.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Proposition</ent>⟦br⟧
